{"tid":1390542,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[會計師] 5/8 工作安排","createTime":"2019-07-31T07:21:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T04:27:10.000Z","uid":77034,"like":79,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"c02621a8c2dd3550f3f64af6a8c946a3537473f2","tid":1390542,"uid":77034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T07:21:36.000Z","msg":"作為專業人員之一的會計師，我覺得事非黑白、不平則鳴是必須要的。<br />\n<br />\n就呢兩個月發生的事情，我都想出一分力。不過，基於有家庭負擔關係未能走到最前線。每一次有活動都會睇住連登，為各位兄弟擔心、怕會出事，睇到兩三點先訓。既然無法走到前線，我都希望在8月5日響應罷工行動。<br />\n<br />\n我係中層人仕，我就同左我條team、同事、朋友講：<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">返工捱夜，近排咁多警暴、警黑事件，有唔舒服可以請日假休息下。睇完醫生，出街行下、坐下，無話病左唔比出街。</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n如果上/中層出聲，絕對會有更多同事和應，也會發覺原來我地絕不孤單。高級經理、經理、Senior，請你們主動出一句聲，出一份力，為香港發聲。我已經做左了，也會繼續做。<br />\n<br />\n兄弟爬山，各有各做！ Be Water !"},{"pid":"21a7e9ac5aaec6d33ccec717762d6ecf8972732e","tid":1390542,"uid":165840,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T07:22:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4e83e9eb5d67e0a6a0404642a34aabf4191097f","tid":1390542,"uid":77034,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"21a7e9ac5aaec6d33ccec717762d6ecf8972732e","tid":1390542,"uid":165840,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T07:22:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T07:25:09.000Z","msg":"會計師朋友，入黎留言、幫推，讓更多人知道有好多人會響應罷工。你們絕不孤單。"},{"pid":"e015970bfcd74be28b40459708124054f8987478","tid":1390542,"uid":77034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T07:27:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b893d428d26b1e2edc2acd33fd002192b81d05d","tid":1390542,"uid":77034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T07:28:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9aebbe3b318327ad9131310963f81bf11e3fc00","tid":1390542,"uid":77034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T07:28:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66b8b7a513e5a0db1bb589559a1cbf73dd3046e4","tid":1390542,"uid":263213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T07:48:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1f1b0573b516e1edf98e33c546391a5e48164d97","tid":1390542,"uid":77034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T09:26:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4395ffd9df0534f7f9e177c62d7839a2e5218008","tid":1390542,"uid":259515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T10:18:47.000Z","msg":"I am Hong Konger. I strike for my home."},{"pid":"508a0a1abe55d9f4ebf65a8ddb9dd06504962bdf","tid":1390542,"uid":77034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T11:43:38.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"b4c0baea693d0ca947eb240c01cdf0682c1cdb2c","tid":1390542,"uid":169836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T11:45:00.000Z","msg":"廢中會計師表示支持"},{"pid":"db2b200038764ab4a88f80577fb997ec2216d3e9","tid":1390542,"uid":286792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T11:45:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"be542f15cc679a8bcdcb91a318fb8e3610658ae0","tid":1390542,"uid":238745,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T11:45:42.000Z","msg":"成日見人係度洗版，日日小組送頭，乜文宣都無哂，唔知做乜鳩。<br />\n<br />\n文宣方向建議如下 : <br />\n1. 集中宣傳建制沒為港人發聲及其他<br />\n2. 全球登報，聲援各地港人<br />\n3. 宣傳8月5日三罷<br />\n4. 重新五點訴求<br />\n5. 平反香港對中國的重要性，自由民主才有利經濟。香港佔中國外資 70%<br />\n6. 宣傳 run and hit, 強烈譴責戀戰行為<br />\n7. 除暴Go<br />\n8. 宣傳年輕一代入獄、移民，所有藍絲家長以後自己照顧自己，共享大灣區榮耀。<br />\n9. 心經簡林、蛇陣長輩圖<br />\n10. 整合多天以後衝擊材料，如醫療系統病人資料不保密、白衣人事、件、濫權、煙花<br />\n11. 支持星火等。。。捐款 (每次行動，比人拉多1x個都死啦。唔該行動前好好考慮法律支援費用仲有幾多係度可以燒)<br />\n12. 其他"},{"pid":"e96163e70d6901a8328dec7330d8323fb8705786","tid":1390542,"uid":102700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"reply